      "content": "i don't even know why i'm still bothering to type this. it feels like everything i've worked for over the last 5 years just... evaporated. the lab results, the funding, the whole identity i built as a researcher. it's all gone. i'm just so incredibly tired. not the kind of tired sleep fixes, but like, a heavy, soul-crushing exhaustion where even breathing feels like too much effort. i just want everything to be quiet. i just want the noise to stop.",
