    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "what do you mean the world isn't safe for me? i'm just sitting in my apartment. it's not a physical safety thing, it's just... everything feels so heavy. like there's no way to actually get that quiet you mentioned. you said to let the rest take me... what does that even mean?",
